The source has been substantially modified from the original, including
renaming the project and module path and restructuring for use as an
osquery extension. Files carrying over from the original work have been
changed.

PackageBeagle does not share git history with the upstream project: it
began as a fresh repository containing the upstream tree at commit
d753592 (2026-06-25). That commit is preserved here as the tag
"bumblebee-base" so the modifications remain reviewable:

    git diff bumblebee-base main

Most files also differ by a mechanical rename applied at import
(bumblebee -> beagle, Bumblebee -> Beagle, BUMBLEBEE -> BEAGLE, and the
module path github.com/perplexityai/bumblebee ->
github.com/packagebeagle/beagle), which accounts for much of that diff
independently of any substantive change.
